fullText: Small meeting - severe rain - [Mr. & Mrs. Holbrook fine here. Didn't come over until 6 P.M. train] - Mrs. La Porte introduced me here
summaryText: Susan B. Anthony attends a small meeting in Logan, Iowa, despite severe rain. She meets with Mrs. J. T. Stern, Mr. & Mrs. Holbrook, and Mrs. La Porte, who introduces her to the group.
